Name: XXX
Description: This exquisite saree is crafted from a subtle blend of cotton and silk. Its elegant off white base pairs perfectly with the intricate ajraak block print in mesmerizing hues of firozi, yellow and maroon. Its delicate beauty and intricate detailing is sure to make you stand out.

Name: YYY
Description: This beige cotton silk saree is adorned with a madhuvani block print in shades of brown and firozi, giving it a subtle and delicate elegance. The fabric shines, giving the outfit an alluring touch of sophistication.

Name: ZZZ
Description: This saree features a beautiful cotton silk fabric in a deep and vibrant red. The art-work is a stunning combination of leafy buildings block print in complementary royalblue and black colors. It's a perfect combination of classic elegance and modern style.

Name: Emerald Wine
Description: Rich malai cotton draped gracefully in a classic saree with a light emerald green base, inlaid with meandering lines of brown and royalblue in striking madhuvani block print pattern. A timeless ensemble for any occasion.

Name: Greenymph
Description: The white cotton saree has a serene beauty. The dark green and light green plant designs, block-printed on it make it look vibrant. The brown border adds a unique charm and enhances the overall look of the saree.

This pure cotton blouse is vivid and captivating. The base color of white is delicately adorned with block printed white flowers on a deep yellow backdrop. Bright and graceful, this blouse is sure to make a statement.

Name: Floral-patli-pallu
Description: This exquisite saree is an ideal combination of grace and beauty. Crafted from pure silk, its immaculate red base is adorned with an exquisite floral block print in shades of yellow, white and green. The border is further enhanced with a subtle print in yellow and green.

Name: Grey-fish-saree
Description: The grey cotton saree is incredibly comfortable to wear. It features a unique layered-tide block print, with beautiful fishes swimming in an ocean of black and maroon. An eye-catching statement piece for any wardrobe.
